blocks.content: Define the function which maps a set ` v ` to the set of proper unordered pairs consisting of exactly two (different) elements of the set ` v ` . (Contributed by AV, 29-Apr-2023.)
blocks.origin:
axiom df-prpr(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3) {
  |- wceq(cprpr, cmpt(s0, universe, cab(s1, wrex(s2, cv(s0), wrex(s3, cv(s0), wa(wne(cv(s2), cv(s3)), wceq(cv(s1), cpr(cv(s2), cv(s3)))))))))
  -| diffss(s2, s3)
  -| diffss(s1, s2)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s1, s3)
  -| diffss(s0, s3)
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
}
blocks.pretty:
axiom df-prpr(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3) {
  ‚ä¢ PrPairs =(s0 ‚àà ùïå ‚Ü¶ { s1 | ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà s0, ‚àÉ(s3 ‚àà s0,(s2 ‚â† s3 ‚àß s1 = { s2, s3 })))})
  ‚ä£ d(s2, s3)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, s2)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s2)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, s3)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s3)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s1)
}

thm prprval(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, class c0, class c1) {
  |- wi(wcel(c0, c1), wceq(cfv(cprpr, c0), cab(s0, wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))))))
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s1, s2)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s0, c1)
  -| diffsc(s1, c0)
  -| diffsc(s1, c1)
  -| diffsc(s2, c0)
  -| diffsc(s2, c1)
} = {
  fvmptd2(hs0, cprpr, c0, cab(s0, wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))), universe, cab(s0, wrex(s1, cv(hs0), wrex(s2, cv(hs0), wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))), universe, wcel(c0, c1))
  df-prpr(hs0, s0, s1, s2)
  adantl(wcel(c0, c1), wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wceq(cab(s0, wrex(s1, cv(hs0), wrex(s2, cv(hs0), wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))), cab(s0, wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))))))
  abbidv(s0, wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wrex(s1, cv(hs0), wrex(s2, cv(hs0), wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))), wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))))
  rexeqbi1dv(s1, cv(hs0), c0, wrex(s2, cv(hs0), wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))), wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))
  rexeq(s2, cv(hs0), c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))
  elex(c0, c1)
  mpdan(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cab(s0, wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))), universe), wral(s1, c0, wcel(cab(s0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))), universe)))
  ralrimivw(s1, c0, wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cab(s0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))), universe))
  mpdan(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cab(s0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))), universe), wral(s2, c0, wcel(cab(s0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))), universe)))
  ralrimivw(s2, c0, wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cab(s0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))), universe))
  sylancr(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cab(s0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))), universe), wss(cab(s0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))), cab(s0, wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))), wcel(cab(s0, wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))), universe))
  ss2abi(s0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))
  simpr(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))
  mp1i(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cab(s0, wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))), universe), weu(s0, wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))
  eueqi(s0, cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))
  zfpair2(s1, s2)
  euabex(s0, wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))

  abrexex2g(s2, s0, c0, c1, universe, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))
  abrexex2g(s1, s0, c0, c1, universe, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(cab(s0, wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))))

  diff.hs0.w(wcel(c0, c1))

  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)

  diffss.ex(s1, hs0)

  diff.cv.s(s0, s1)
  diff.cv.s(s0, s2)

thm prprval(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, class c0, class c1) {
  ‚ä¢ (c0 ‚àà c1 ‚Üí(PrPairs ` c0)= { s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))})
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s1)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s2)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, s2)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, c1)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, c1)
  ‚ä£ d(s2, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s2, c1)
} = {
  fvmptd2(hs0, cprpr, c0, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))}, universe, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà hs0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà hs0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))}, universe, c0 ‚àà c1)
  df-prpr(hs0, s0, s1, s2)
  adantl(c0 ‚àà c1, hs0 = c0, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà hs0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà hs0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))} = { s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))})
  abbidv(s0, hs0 = c0, ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà hs0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà hs0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))), ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))))
  rexeqbi1dv(s1, hs0, c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà hs0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })), ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))
  rexeq(s2, hs0, c0, (s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))
  elex(c0, c1)
  mpdan(c0 ‚àà c1, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))} ‚àà ùïå, ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà c0, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))} ‚àà ùïå))
  ralrimivw(s1, c0, c0 ‚àà c1, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))} ‚àà ùïå)
  mpdan(c0 ‚àà c1, { s0 | ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))} ‚àà ùïå, ‚àÄ(s2 ‚àà c0, { s0 |(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })} ‚àà ùïå))
  ralrimivw(s2, c0, c0 ‚àà c1, { s0 |(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })} ‚àà ùïå)
  sylancr(c0 ‚àà c1, { s0 |(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })} ‚àà ùïå, { s0 |(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })} ‚äÜ { s0 | s0 = { s1, s2 } }, { s0 | s0 = { s1, s2 } } ‚àà ùïå)
  ss2abi(s0, (s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }), s0 = { s1, s2 })
  simpr(s1 ‚â† s2, s0 = { s1, s2 })
  mp1i(c0 ‚àà c1, { s0 | s0 = { s1, s2 } } ‚àà ùïå, ‚àÉ!(s0, s0 = { s1, s2 }))
  eueqi(s0, { s1, s2 })
  zfpair2(s1, s2)
  euabex(s0, s0 = { s1, s2 })
  ssexg({ s0 |(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })}, { s0 | s0 = { s1, s2 } }, universe)
  abrexex2g(s2, s0, c0, c1, universe, (s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 }))
  abrexex2g(s1, s0, c0, c1, universe, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c({ s0 | ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s2 ‚àà c0,(s1 ‚â† s2 ‚àß s0 = { s1, s2 })))})
  diff.hs0.c(universe)
  diff.hs0.w(c0 ‚àà c1)
  diff.wceq.s(s0, hs0, c0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.cv.s(s1, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s1, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s1)
  diff.cv.s(s2, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s2, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s2)
  diff.wcel.s(s1, c0, c1)
  diff.wcel.s(s2, c0, c1)
  diff.cpr.s(s0, s1, s2)
  diff.cv.s(s0, s1)
  diff.cv.s(s0, s2)
  diffss.ex(s2, s0)
  diff.universe.s(s2)
  diff.universe.s(s0)
  diffss.ex(s1, s0)
  diff.universe.s(s1)
}

  pm4.71ri(wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))), wcel(cv(s0), cpw(c0)))

  prssi(cv(s1), c0, cv(s2))

  adantl(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))), wb(wcel(cv(s0), cpw(c0)), wcel(cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)), cpw(c0))))

  a1i(wcel(c0, c1), wb(wcel(cv(s0), cfv(cprpr, c0)), wa(wcel(cv(s0), cfv(cspr, c0)), wceq(cfv(chash, cv(s0)), nat2))))

blocks.name: reuprpr
blocks.content: There is a unique proper unordered pair fulfilling a wff iff there are uniquely two different sets fulfilling a corresponding wff. (Contributed by AV, 30-Apr-2023.)
blocks.origin:
thm reuprpr(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3, setvar s4, class c0, class c1, wff w0, wff w1, wff w2) {
  |- wi(wcel(c0, c1), wb(wreu(s0, cfv(cprpr, c0), w0), wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, w3a(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), w1, wral(s3, c0, wral(s4, c0, wi(wa(wne(cv(s3), cv(s4)), w2), wceq(cpr(cv(s3), cv(s4)), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)))))))))))
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))), wb(w0, w1))
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s3), cv(s4))), wb(w0, w2))
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s0, s3)
  -| diffss(s0, s4)
  -| diffss(s1, s2)
  -| diffss(s1, s3)
  -| diffss(s1, s4)
  -| diffss(s2, s3)
  -| diffss(s2, s4)
  -| diffss(s3, s4)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s0, c1)
  -| diffsc(s1, c0)
  -| diffsc(s1, c1)
  -| diffsc(s2, c0)
  -| diffsc(s2, c1)
  -| diffsc(s3, c0)
  -| diffsc(s3, c1)
  -| diffsc(s4, c0)
  -| diffsc(s4, c1)
  -| diffsw(s0, w1)
  -| diffsw(s0, w2)
  -| diffsw(s1, w0)
  -| diffsw(s2, w0)
  -| diffsw(s3, w0)
  -| diffsw(s4, w0)
} = {
  3bitrd(wcel(c0, c1), wreu(s0, cfv(cprpr, c0), w0), wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, w3a(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), w1, wral(s3, c0, wral(s4, c0, wi(wa(wne(cv(s3), cv(s4)), w2), wceq(cpr(cv(s3), cv(s4)), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))))), wreu(s0, cfv(cspr, c0), wa(wceq(cfv(chash, cv(s0)), nat2), w0)), wrex(s1, c0, wrex(s2, c0, wa(wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), w1), wral(s3, c0, wral(s4, c0, wi(wa(wne(cv(s3), cv(s4)), w2), wceq(cpr(cv(s3), cv(s4)), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))))))))))
  prprsprreu(s0, c0, c1, w0)
  reupr(s0, s1, s2, s3, s4, c0, c1, wa(wceq(cfv(chash, cv(s0)), nat2), w0), wa(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), w1), wa(wne(cv(s3), cv(s4)), w2))
  anbi12d(wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))), wceq(cfv(chash, cv(s0)), nat2), w0, wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), w1)
  syl6bbr(wceq(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))), wceq(cfv(chash, cv(s0)), nat2), wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cfv(chash, cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))), nat2))
  fveqeq2(cv(s0), cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2)), chash, nat2)
  el2v(s1, s2, wb(wne(cv(s1), cv(s2)), wceq(cfv(chash, cpr(cv(s1), cv(s2))), nat2)))
  hashprg(cv(s1), universe, cv(s2), universe)

blocks.name: 2exopprim
blocks.content: The existence of an ordered pair fulfilling a wff implies the existence of an unordered pair fulfilling the wff. (Contributed by AV, 29-Jul-2023.)

blocks.name: reuopreuprim
blocks.content: There is a unique unordered pair with ordered elements fulfilling a wff if there is a unique ordered pair fulfilling the wff. (Contributed by AV, 28-Jul-2023.)
